,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"（でも、きっと……わたしがほしいものもある……\nもっと上手に演奏が……できるようになりたい……\nそうなれたら、今よりわたしは強くなれる気がする……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event156-15-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"（そう思うと……不安はすっと消えていく……\n音楽の中にいる時……世界と繋がってるって……\nわたしは強く思えるから……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event156-15-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"リサ","body":"（ステージの上から見えるこの景色……\nどこまでも遠くまで、お客さんの姿がよく見える。\nアタシ、やっぱり好きだな、ここから見える景色）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event156-15-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"リサ","body":"（こんなふうに感じられるようになったのは、\nアタシをお節介焼きの友希那の幼馴染から、\nRoseliaのベーシストにしてくれたみんなのおかげ）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event156-15-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"リサ","body":"（これから先も、この光景を何度でも見たい。\nRoseliaのみんなと一緒にいつまでも……！）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motio